  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "LkYsROj5kzayizxYXa40JuUwuaw=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:33.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# Drive Manifest Feed Structure\n\nThe drive manifest feed lives at topic `ph:v2:drive:<driveId>` and is owned by the drive creator's signer. Each feed index resolves to encrypted JSON on `/bytes`.\n\n## Schema\n\n```json\n{\n  \"driveId\": \"drive-abc\",\n  \"name\": \"Finance Drive\",\n  \"documents\": {\n    \"doc-001\": {\n      \"documentType\": \"powerhouse/budget-statement\",\n      \"name\": \"Q1 Budget\",\n      \"parentFolder\": \"folder-reports\",\n      \"lastUpdated\": \"2026-04-10T12:01:00Z\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"folders\": {\n    \"folder-reports\": { \"name\": \"Reports\" }\n  },\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2026-04-10T12:02:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n## Role\n\n- Indexes every document the drive contains and the folder tree\n- `parentFolder` on a document lets clients reconstruct the folder hierarchy\n- One drive manifest feed per drive, one feed index per update\n",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:33.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:33.000Z"
    }
  },
